<item>
            <title>[LU-16523] Adjust the format of rename_stats</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16523</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the header of rename_stats is like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-yaml&quot;&gt;
rename_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;stats: &lt;/span&gt;
-
&#160; snapshot_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;time: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;1234567890&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;123456789&lt;/span&gt;
&#160; start_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;time: &lt;/span&gt;&#160; &#160;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;1234567880&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;987654321&lt;/span&gt;
&#160; elapsed_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;time: &lt;/span&gt;&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;135802468&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Change it to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-yaml&quot;&gt;
rename_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;stats: &lt;/span&gt;
- snapshot_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;time: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;1234567890&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;123456789&lt;/span&gt;
- start_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;time: &lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;1234567880&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;987654321&lt;/span&gt;
- elapsed_&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;time: &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;135802468&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Both are valid YAML but the latter is more friendly to human.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
